Description: Limestone ostracon: on the recto seven lines of an incomplete (upper left missing) literary text (a hymn to Mut?). On the verso three mostly faded lines of a text of unknown character (literary or a hymn).
Bibliographic references: Trismegistos / An interdisciplinary portal of papyrological and epigraphic resources (393037) (http://www.trismegistos.org/text/393037)
